## üöÄ Features

- ‚úÖ Auto-square images with optional blurred/solid/gradient padding
- üñºÔ∏è Add customizable **rounded borders** around photos
- ‚úçÔ∏è Annotate left/right/top/bottom with vertical or centered text (great for branding)
- üìÑ Generate auto-arranged **A4 collage pages** from processed photos
- üìê Resize final output by target size (e.g. `--size 5.5x5.5cm` or `--size 55x55mm`)
- üß™ Includes CLI, Makefile, tests, and PyPI packaging

---

## üì¶ Requirements

- Python `>= 3.7`
- `opencv-python`
- `numpy`

---

## üîß Installation

```bash
pip install softcropper
```

For local development:

```bash
make venv
make install
```

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è CLI Usage

```bash
softcropper ./input_photos --mode blur --border --text \
  --left "@CanvaMagnet" \
  --right "+971 545800462" \
  --top "Preview" \
  --bottom "www.CanvaMagnet.com" \
  --size 5.5x5.5cm \
  --a4
```

### Options

| Flag           | Description                                               |
|----------------|-----------------------------------------------------------|
| `--mode`       | One of: `blur` (default), `solid`, `gradient`             |
| `--border`     | Add rounded frame around photo                            |
| `--text`       | Enable text mode (requires at least one `--left/right/top/bottom`) |
| `--left`       | Vertical text on left side                                |
| `--right`      | Vertical text on right side                               |
| `--top`        | Centered text above the image                             |
| `--bottom`     | Centered text below the image                             |
| `--size`       | Resize output image (supports `mm` or `cm`, e.g. `55x55mm`) |
| `--a4`         | Generate A4 page(s) from processed images                 |

---

## ‚úÖ Testing

```bash
make test
```

Or manually:

```bash
PYTEST_DISABLE_PLUGIN_AUTOLOAD=1 pytest tests/ -v
```

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Makefile Commands

```bash
make venv         # Create .venv
make install      # Install locally in editable mode
make test         # Run tests
make build        # Build wheel and source dist
make deploy       # Deploy to PyPI
make clean        # Remove virtualenv + build artifacts
```

